## 1. Introduction

This report provides the results of testing **BiponyShop**, an e-commerce platform. Testing was conducted for user registration, cart functionality, and checkout process.

---

## 2. Test Results

| Module Name       | Status    | Defects Found |
|-------------------|-----------|---------------|
| User Registration | Passed    | 0             |
| Product Catalog   | Passed    | 0             |
| Cart & Checkout   | Failed    | 2             |

---

## 3. Metrics
- **Total Test Cases**: 15
- **Executed Test Cases**: 15
- **Passed**: 13
- **Failed**: 2

---

## 4. Defects Found

| Bug ID | Severity | Status   | Description                    |
|--------|----------|----------|--------------------------------|
| BUG-01 | High     | Open     | Cannot proceed to checkout     |
| BUG-02 | Medium   | Closed   | Cart does not update with quantity changes |

---

## 5. Environment
- **OS**: Windows 10
- **Browsers**: Chrome (v91), Firefox (v89)

---

## 6. Summary

**BiponyShop** passed most of the tests, with issues related to checkout functionality. Critical defects must be fixed to proceed with production release.

